Sentencas: Sm, In co-doped ceria Ce0.80Sm0.20-xInxO1.90 (SDCI) series (x = 0, 0.075, 0.10, 0.15) are fabricated, aiming to evaluate the doping effect of In on the electrolyte performance of Ce0.80Sm0.2O1.90 (SDC).
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: XRD is employed to characterize the structure of the Sm, In co-doped ceria.
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The symmetrical cells and single cells consisting of Sm, In co-doped ceria is fabricated and analyzed via electrochemical impedance spectra and I-V diagram.
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The proportion of Ce3+ and Ce4+ in SDCI is investigated by XPS.
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The results of multiple analysis approaches indicate that the electrical performance of Sm, In co-doping ceria is enhanced.
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The maximum power density of cells fabricated by SDCI is improved on condition that the concentration of In is below 10 mol%.
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Sm, In co-doping is proved to be a promising avenue to improve the ionic conductivity and catalytic activity of ceria.
Titulo: The co-doping effect of Sm and In on ceria for electrolyte application in IT-SOFC
